'''Cade''' may refer to:

==[[Canon]]==
*'''[[Cade]]''', a [[clone trooper]] present at the [[Attack on Kamino]].

==[[Star Wars Legends|''Star Wars'' Legends]]==
*'''[[Cade Skywalker]]''', a [[Bounty hunter/Legends|bounty hunter]], [[Pirate/Legends|pirate]] and former [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]]; a descendant of [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke]] and [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Anakin Skywalker]].
*'''[[Cade Umarian]]''', a pirate who was active during the [[Galactic Civil War/Legends|Galactic Civil War]].

